---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="How we built GROOMO.cz"
  description="Case study: complete brand creation and Shopify e-shop for GROOMO.cz — from naming through visual identity to unique dog breed-based product filtering."
  lang="en"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="case-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-blob"></div>
    <div class="container case-hero-inner">
      <p class="case-label">Case Study</p>
      <h1>How we built <a href="https://groomo.cz" class="groomo-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GROOMO.cz</a></h1>
      <p class="case-perex">Dominika Elliot — an experienced groomer and owner of a popular dog salon — wanted to expand into e-commerce. She knew what customers needed. We knew how to deliver it. Together, we built a brand and Shopify store unlike anything on the Czech market.</p>
      <div class="hero-tags">
        <span class="tag">Brand</span>
        <span class="tag">Shopify</span>
        <span class="tag">E-shop</span>
        <span class="tag">Breed Filtering</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GROOMO brand -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <h2 class="section-center-heading">GROOMO brand</h2>
      <div class="brand-logo-grid">
        <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--left">
          <img src="/groomo-logo-imgnavysku-wh.png" alt="GROOMO mascot — portrait" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--c1">
          <img src="/groomo-logo-imgbasictext-wh.png" alt="GROOMO logo with tagline" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--c2">
          <img src="/groomo-logo-basic-blu.png" alt="GROOMO wordmark" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--c3">
          <img src="/groomo-logo-imgbasic-wh.png" alt="GROOMO logo with icon" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--right">
          <img src="/groomoinstitut-logo-imgnavysku-wh-1.png" alt="GROOMO Institut logo" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="brand-hero-wrap">
        <div class="brand-hero-bg"></div>
        <h4 class="brand-hero-caption">A brand and e-shop<br />built with love for dogs.</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Brand text -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary">
    <div class="container text-col">
      <h3 class="section-subheading">About the name</h3>
      <p class="section-text">The brand and name were a real challenge. We had to choose between ideas like "psikrasa.cz" (which described the concept well but offered little room for a logo) and something rooted in the internationally recognized word GROOMING — even if it's not common in Czech and the domains were long gone.</p>
      <p class="section-text">Choosing an AI-colored dog as an avatar was equally controversial, but in a world flooded with beautiful dog photography we wanted something that would stand apart and immediately signal this isn't just another hobby shop. Colors settled, geometric shapes followed — and the whole show was underway.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- E-shop for serious dog owners -->
  <section class="section bg-elevated">
    <div class="container content-split">
      <div class="content-text">
        <h2 class="section-heading">An e-shop for serious dog owners</h2>
        <p class="section-text">GROOMO.cz was never meant to be just another online store. Dominika wanted it to become a guide and advisor that even the most experienced dog breeders could rely on.</p>
        <p class="section-text">So alongside products we built a blog where experts write about topics dog owners actually care about. The inspiration came from salon practice and thorough keyword analysis. Articles answer real questions: <em>"What to do when a dog keeps scratching?"</em> <em>"How to handle alopecia?"</em> <em>"How to prepare a dog for a show?"</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-img">
        <img src="/groomo-filter.webp" alt="GROOMO.cz — e-shop for serious dog owners" class="section-img" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GROOMO Institut -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-center-heading">GROOMO Institut</h2>
      <p class="section-text centered">Part of the overall plan was a course section offering training for professional groomers as well as lessons for dog and cat owners. The Institut gave Dominika's expertise a new dimension: she was no longer just a seller, but an authority in the field.</p>
      <div class="institut-img-wrap">
        <img src="/menu.png" alt="GROOMO navigation — Institut section" class="institut-img" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <blockquote class="cs-quote">
        <p>"Thanks to the GROOMO Institut page, my courses took off immediately — I didn't know where to turn first."</p>
        <cite>— Dominika Elliot, GROOMO.cz</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Shopify and breed filtering -->
  <section class="section bg-elevated">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-center-heading">Shopify — and then some</h2>
      <p class="section-text centered">We made extensive design and functionality customizations to the theme — menus, advanced filtering, labels — all configured so the e-shop team can manage it independently. The volume of brands and product sub-groups was a challenge. But the biggest innovation is <strong class="hl">dog breed filtering</strong> — likely unique on the Czech market. Pick a breed and the store recommends shampoos, brushes, or treats ideal for your dog.</p>
      <div class="shopify-img-wrap">
        <img src="/podle-plemene-groomocz.png" alt="Dog breed selection on GROOMO.cz" class="section-img" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <blockquote class="cs-quote">
        <p>"I wanted every dog owner to easily find what their pet needs. Breed filtering makes that possible."</p>
        <cite>— Dominika Elliot, GROOMO.cz</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Find your breed banner -->
  <section class="tribe-banner">
    <div class="container tribe-inner">
      <div class="tribe-text">
        <h3 class="tribe-label">Find<br />your<br />breed</h3>
      </div>
      <img src="/moje-plemeno-in-black.png" alt="GROOMO — my breed, dark mode" class="tribe-img" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content that helps and sells -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary">
    <div class="container content-split">
      <div class="content-text">
        <h3 class="section-heading-sm">Content that helps and sells</h3>
        <p class="section-text">Blog, courses, and guides make this an e-shop that's about more than just selling. Customers return for advice — and along the way buy products recommended by an expert, or suggested by Shopify based on their inputs.</p>
        <p class="section-text">This builds trust and organically increases average order value. Content isn't a cost — it's an investment that pays off.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-img">
        <img src="/clanek-blog-groomo-cz.png" alt="GROOMO blog — content that helps and sells" class="section-img" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Customer reviews -->
  <section class="section bg-elevated reviews-section">
    <div class="container reviews-wrap">
      <div class="stars-row" aria-label="5 out of 5 rating">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="reviews-label">Customers say</p>
      <p class="reviews-caption">Rated by customers on Heureka</p>
      <div class="reviews-grid">
        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="review-text">"Breed filtering is an absolute game changer. Finally I know what to buy for my Corgi."</p>
          <span class="review-author">— GROOMO.cz customer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="review-text">"Beautiful shop, fast shipping, products perfectly matched to my breed. Won't shop anywhere else."</p>
          <span class="review-author">— GROOMO.cz customer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="review-text">"The blog is brilliant — genuinely expert content. Finally an e-shop that truly understands dogs."</p>
          <span class="review-author">— GROOMO.cz customer</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Price vs performance -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary">
    <div class="container text-col">
      <h3 class="section-heading-sm">Price vs. performance — $$$</h3>
      <p class="section-text">The most expensive option isn't always the best. Shopify combined with smart theme customizations and thoughtful content strategy delivered results that custom development would have cost many times more to achieve — and still couldn't match what Shopify offers out of the box.</p>
      <p class="section-text">Breed filtering? Done via Shopify tags and smart collections. Professional blog? Shopify Pages with a custom template. Courses? A customer section linking to an education platform. All of it without a single line of custom backend code.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="section bg-elevated">
    <div class="container text-col">
      <h3 class="section-heading-sm">Results</h3>
      <p class="section-text">The GROOMO e-shop launched in November 2024. Within the first weeks it generated a wave of registrations and strong positive feedback from customers and professionals alike.</p>
      <p class="section-text">The biggest impact came from breed filtering — simplifying the buying process for owners while making GROOMO an e-shop with no equal on the Czech market.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Conclusion -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary">
    <div class="container text-col">
      <h3 class="section-heading-sm">And the takeaway?</h3>
      <p class="section-text">It started with an idea that took clear shape over a few meetings. In four months — through the collaboration of the aethero team — it became a modern Shopify e-shop with a distinct identity, unique features, and content that serves both casual owners and professionals.</p>
      <p class="section-text">GROOMO is no longer just a store. It's a brand that connects products, education, and expertise — and that's what makes it stand apart in the world of pet e-commerce.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery -->
  <section class="section bg-elevated gallery-section">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <h3 class="section-center-heading-sm">Gallery</h3>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <img src="/hp-groomo-cz.png" alt="GROOMO — e-shop homepage" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/groomo-filter.webp" alt="GROOMO — breed-based filtering" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/menu.png" alt="GROOMO — navigation" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/podle-plemene-groomocz.png" alt="GROOMO — breed selection" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/moje-plemeno-in-black.png" alt="GROOMO — my breed" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/clanek-blog-groomo-cz.png" alt="GROOMO — blog for dog owners" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .case-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 200px 0 100px;
    background: #07051B;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
    background-image: url('/ae-bgr-w-glass-b-2x-v3.webp');
    background-size: cover; background-position: center bottom;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .hero-blob {
    position: absolute; top: -10%; right: -5%;
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(203,0,215,0.18) 0%, rgba(9,32,102,0.25) 50%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(60px); pointer-events: none;
  }
  .case-hero-inner {
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    max-width: 860px;
  }
  .case-label {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--action); text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }
  .case-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(42px, 5.5vw, 76px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-32); color: #fff;
  }
  .groomo-link {
    color: var(--action); text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .groomo-link:hover { opacity: 0.8; }
  .case-perex {
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.6vw, 21px); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 1.65; max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-40);
  }
  .hero-tags {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .tag {
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: rgba(13,212,205,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(13,212,205,0.25);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--action);
  }

  /* ─── SHARED ─── */
  /* Case study = reading viewport, -20% vs standard */
  .container { max-width: 1024px; }
  .container-wide { max-width: 1152px; }

  .section { padding: var(--space-120) 0; }
  .bg-elevated { background: var(--bg-elevated); }
  .bg-secondary { background: var(--bg-secondary); }
  .section-text {
    font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82); line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-24); max-width: 760px;
  }
  .section-text.centered { max-width: 780px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center; }
  .section-text .hl { color: var(--action); font-weight: 700; }
  .section-img { width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: var(--radius-md); display: block; }

  .section-center-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 700; color: #fff; text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
  }
  .section-center-heading-sm {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: clamp(24px, 2.8vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 700; color: #fff; text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
  }
  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 46px);
    font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: var(--space-32);
  }
  .section-heading-sm {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: var(--space-32);
  }
  .section-subheading {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: clamp(20px, 2vw, 30px);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--action); margin-bottom: var(--space-24);
  }
  .text-col { max-width: 780px; }

  /* ─── BRAND section ─── */
  .brand-logo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.3fr 0.85fr;
    grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr);
    height: 400px;
    gap: 2px;
    background: #07051B;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
  }
  .logo-cell {
    background: #000326;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px 20px;
  }
  .logo-cell--left  { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 1 / 4; }
  .logo-cell--right { grid-column: 3; grid-row: 1 / 4; }
  .logo-cell--c1    { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 1; }
  .logo-cell--c2    { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 2; }
  .logo-cell--c3    { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 3; }
  .logo-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }
  .logo-cell--left .logo-img,
  .logo-cell--right .logo-img {
    height: 100%;
    width: auto;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  /* ─── BRAND HERO IMAGE (CSS background) ─── */
  .brand-hero-wrap {
    position: relative; height: 480px; overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: var(--space-40);
  }
  .brand-hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/groomo-mainheader011.png');
    background-size: cover; background-position: center top;
  }
  .brand-hero-caption {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 48px;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;
    color: #fff; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,3,38,0.5);
    max-width: 340px;
  }

  /* ─── CONTENT SPLIT ─── */
  .content-split {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px; align-items: center;
  }
  .content-img {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden; border-radius: var(--radius-md); max-height: 500px;
  }
  .content-img .section-img {
    width: 100%; height: 500px; object-fit: cover; object-position: top;
  }

  /* ─── INSTITUT ─── */
  .institut-img-wrap {
    max-width: 860px; margin: var(--space-48) auto; overflow: hidden; border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }
  .institut-img {
    width: 100%; height: 420px; object-fit: cover; object-position: top; display: block;
  }

  /* ─── SHOPIFY ─── */
  .shopify-img-wrap {
    max-width: 900px; margin: var(--space-48) auto; overflow: hidden; border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }
  .shopify-img-wrap .section-img {
    height: 520px; object-fit: cover; object-position: top;
  }

  /* ─── QUOTE ─── */
  .cs-quote {
    margin: var(--space-48) auto 0;
    max-width: 660px; text-align: center;
    border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    padding-top: var(--space-40);
  }
  .cs-quote p {
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 24px); font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }
  .cs-quote cite {
    font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; color: var(--action);
    font-weight: 600; display: block;
  }

  /* ─── TRIBE BANNER ─── */
  .tribe-banner {
    background: var(--action);
    padding: 60px 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .tribe-inner {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 48px;
  }
  .tribe-text { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .tribe-label {
    display: block; font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5.5vw, 72px); font-weight: 700;
    color: #000326; line-height: 1.05; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .tribe-img {
    width: 100%; max-width: 580px; height: 240px;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md); display: block;
  }

  /* ─── REVIEWS ─── */
  .reviews-section { padding: var(--space-80) 0; }
  .reviews-wrap { text-align: center; }
  .stars-row {
    font-size: 48px; color: #FFD700;
    letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }
  .reviews-label {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  .reviews-caption {
    font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-64);
  }
  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-24); text-align: left;
  }
  .review-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-32);
  }
  .review-stars {
    font-size: 18px; color: #FFD700;
    letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }
  .review-text {
    font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }
  .review-author {
    font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ─── GALLERY ─── */
  .gallery-section { padding-bottom: var(--space-120); }
  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-16);
    grid-auto-rows: 260px;
  }
  .gallery-img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm); display: block;
  }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .content-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-40); }
    .tribe-inner { flex-direction: column; }
    .tribe-img { max-width: 100%; height: 200px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .case-hero { padding: 140px 0 60px; }
    .reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-auto-rows: 180px; }
  }
</style>
